wdi2-TG.VAL.TOTL.GD.ZS.def: Merchandise trade as a share of GDP is the sum of merchandise exports and imports divided by the value of GDP, all in current U.S. dollars.
wdi2-TG.VAL.TOTL.GD.ZS.name: Merchandise trade
wdi2-TG.VAL.TOTL.GD.ZS.source: World Trade Organization, and World Bank GDP estimates.
